name: "Lost Baby"
description:
This photo was taken in Bandung, Indonesia, during the celebration of Indonesian independence in 2018. I spotted a stroller alone at the moment, with no one near him.

It reminds me of a child alone in the big wide world. You don't have free will over your life as a youngster until you're old enough to make your own decisions. In an ever-expanding universe, we will always be lost babies.
